valid_dep_types.name: valid_dep_types
valid_dep_types.value:
-- Allow:
        -- 1. Function -> Function
        -- 2. Endpoint -> Function
        -- Prevent:
        -- 1. Function -> Endpoint
        -- 2. Endpoint -> Endpoint
        dependency_type = 'function' AND
        (dependent_type = 'function' OR dependent_type = 'endpoint')
